  "commit_message": "HeaderMatch: fix type error\n\nlivecheck's `HeaderMatch` strategy works with data from\n`Strategy.page_headers`, which calls `Utils::Curl.curl_headers`, which\ncalls `Curl.parse_curl_output`, which calls `Curl.parse_curl_response`\nand that determines the structure of header hash objects.\n`parse_curl_response` handles headers that appear more than once in a\nresponse by setting the hash value to an array. However, the `headers`\nparameter type in `HeaderMatch.versions_from_content` only expects a\nhash ",
